      <p>Whether you're framing a house at night, finishing drywall in a basement, or running underground conduit in a trench, the right job site light makes the difference between fast, accurate work and frustrating, error-prone labor. But with hundreds of work lights on Amazon, comparing them side by side is a chore most contractors don't have time for.</p>
      <p>We've gathered 8 of the highest-rated job site lights on Amazon — including tripod lights, string lights, portable work lights, and battery-powered options — and compared them by brightness, durability, portability, power source, and value. Here's the full breakdown.</p>

      <h2>Comparison Methodology</h2>
      <p>Every light on this list was evaluated based on: verified buyer ratings, lumen output, IP weather rating, power source (corded, battery, or both), build quality, portability, and value at its current price point. All links go directly to Amazon for current pricing and availability.</p>

