      <p><strong>ASIN:</strong> B077ZCTBFY</p>
      <p>The <a href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B077ZCTBFY?tag=sciencesolved-20" rel="nofollow sponsored" target="_blank">DEWALT DCL079B</a> is the highest-rated job site light in our lineup at 4.8 stars — and for good reason. It delivers 3000 lumens of bright LED light with three selectable modes (high, medium, low) and mounts on a sturdy tripod stand. Being battery-powered (DEWALT 20V MAX system), it goes anywhere on site without dragging extension cords.</p>
      <p>Contractors who already own DEWALT 20V tools will appreciate battery compatibility — use the same 5Ah batteries that power your impact driver and circular saw. The tripod extends high enough for room lighting and collapses compactly for truck storage. It's the ultimate cordless convenience pick.</p>
      <p><strong>Best for:</strong> DEWALT tool owners, cordless job sites, remodels with no power, quick setup/teardown.</p>
      <p><a href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B077ZCTBFY?tag=sciencesolved-20" rel="nofollow sponsored" target="_blank">→ Check current price on Amazon</a></p>

